Maintainer: Kai Gu <gukai1212@163.com>
Description: It's a complement to 'mcr' package, contains functions to 
    quantify or quality the relation between two measurement methods with 
    the referring to CLSI recommendations, making it easier to apply common 
    analysis in In Vitro Diagnostic Trials. 
